{"tid":1278092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重要既要講十萬次 千祈唔好道歉","createTime":"2019-07-02T10:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T12:41:30.000Z","uid":269052,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0de36b62c278cff06ed67406dae23b285009e67c","tid":1278092,"uid":269052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:59:36.000Z","msg":"我以前係絕對和理非<br />\n我想講<br />\n琴晚既行動其實中和左好多和理非<br />\n好多和理非都開始理解勇武既必要<br />\n<br />\n係 好多團體可以出黎譴責你<br />\n但唔代表你地失去左支持<br />\n琴晚係整場運動新既一頁<br />\n如果道歉就乜撚都推翻哂<br />\n<br />\n同埋 整爛玻璃道乜撚野歉<br />\n林鄭同中央都未跪低 邊度到我地要道歉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕不道歉<br />\n絕不妥協</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後要多謝琴晚一班義士<br />\n廢中如我今日每次睇片都不斷流馬尿<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你地係香港既希望</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好好休息 香港需要你"},{"pid":"760f4e1ba47b0722348ea778f79a1bc5da269097","tid":1278092,"uid":106072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:04:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8e0019da31e337af2d02ff112f1b786e6dfe1f21","tid":1278092,"uid":176550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:10:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"caf979b94424100b525a8f85da1637127cdf190a","tid":1278092,"uid":81725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:11:04.000Z","msg":"push！！！"},{"pid":"512e321ad8d1bcd7d427fce8a6ffa3f4adc109d2","tid":1278092,"uid":60563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:11:46.000Z","msg":"暴政迫死我地3個同數唔清既義士流血<br />\n佢唔道歉我地道乜撚野歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d94d79c6d5819d9